title: Bisexuality & Dudes Being Vulnerable ft. Kelsey Darragh
description:
We welcome our favorite bisexual boss bitch onto the pod this week - Kelsey Darragh. She speaks to her experience of being queer in a small town, breaking free and finding happiness with her open relationship. We confirm the ultimate technique to making dudes feel vulnerable.
